description: Naters Taters is the ultimate fresh cut fries food stand. They are cooking up the finest cuts with optional towering toppings cheese, bacon and steak. The best price and generous portions you can't beat anywhere. Follow your nose to Naters Taters, the place to go for the ultimate fresh cut fries lover served by proud friendly staff, you will walk away with a full satisfied stomach.
name: Naters Taters
